WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:06.029 --> 00:00:11.928
I was told, once you become a mom, there is
no time for yourself.

00:00:11.928 --> 00:00:18.389
Any free time that you might have, should
be spent cleaning, sleeping and planning out

00:00:18.389 --> 00:00:23.009
the rest of your day.

00:00:23.009 --> 00:00:28.289
Other Mothers told me that gaining weight
was apart of Mother hood and I should just

00:00:28.289 --> 00:00:32.809
accept it — be okay with it and never mind
it.

00:00:32.809 --> 00:01:02.119
I remember one mom telling me no one is going
to care anyway.

00:01:02.119 --> 00:02:44.409
Well, I care…

00:02:44.409 --> 00:02:47.229
What empowers me while working out?

00:02:47.229 --> 00:02:49.909
Knowing that I can do both!

00:02:49.909 --> 00:03:03.628
I will what I want.

